HEADWORD: Monastical
<hw>Mo*nas"tic*al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/ monk: cf. F.
<ets>monastique</ets>. See <er>Monastery</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn>
